"```sql\nSELECT posts.Body\nFROM tags\nJOIN posts ON tags.ExcerptPostId = posts.Id\nWHERE tags.Count = (SELECT MAX(Count) FROM tags);\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the body of the post from which the most popular tag is excerpted. It uses a subquery to find the maximum count of tags, which indicates the most popular tag, and then joins the `tags` table with the `posts` table using the `ExcerptPostId` to get the corresponding post body."